Installation is straightforward.

For cap text support, optionally install libcap:

	http://www.kernel.org/pub/linux/libs/security/linux-privs/kernel-2.4/libcap-1.10.tar.gz

Untar the sources:

	$ tar -zxf cage-0.80.tar.gz

Change into the source directory:

	$ cd cage-0.80

Configure it:

	$ ./configure

Make and install the binary and man page:

	# make install

Setup POSIX 1003.1e behavior:

	http://original.killa.net/infosec/caps.html or README.caps
